docker service rollback client ----------------------------------> 

for suppose if we have one version its called as version1 
and next if we created a new version means it will be version2
now if we rollbacked means the version version version3 will be get created and we go to the application in version2
now again if we rollbacked means the version that means we want previous version means  version4 will be get created and we go to the application in version3
if we are doing no.of times rollback means we will go to a previous version & newly created version only 
Not like that we want particularly first version only the original version means we need to do upgrate the image


